headline: Pinnacle West Sets Date for 2025 Third-Quarter Financial Results, Webcast/Conference Call
summary: PHOENIX, October 02, 2025--Pinnacle West Capital Corp. plans to release its 2025 third-quarter financial results before U.S. financial markets open on Monday, Nov. 3, 2025.
